              <img src="/assets/logo.png" alt=""/>
            </div>
            <div class="list-info">
              <div class="list-doctor-info">
                <span class="doctor-name"><a href="#">路人甲</a></span>
                <span class="doctor-lv">主治医师</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="doctor-intro">
              医生简介：
              <p>
                这里是对医生的简介，可以写一些医生擅长的症状啊～
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="doctor-time">
              <p>未来可预约的前五个工作时段：</p>
              <div class="work-time morning">
                <span class="work-date">11/11</span>
                <span class="week">星期几</span>
              </div>
              <div class="work-time afternoon">
